quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,78,"O wi'i: \"Ko mi okkiraa …óum, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii\". E o anndaa wonnde gom…óii Alla halkiino gire, adii…ìe mo, …ìur…ìe doole, …ìuri mo …óuu…óude jawle? ∆Åe lamndoytaake fii junuubi ma…ì…ìe, kam…ìe bom…ìe …ìen"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yim…ìe makko …ìen, cu…óaari makko ndin. Yi…óu…ìe nguurndam aduna …ìen wi'i: \"Hara nun men he…ìayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. Kanko on, pellet, ko o jom-ge…ìal mawnungal"
  28,80,"Okkaa…ìe ganndal …ìen kan wi'i: \"Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on gom…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i\". Kono hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  28,81,"Men mutindini mo e galle makko …óen, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko faaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano faabotoo…óo hoore-mun"
  28,82,"∆Åen yelinoo…ìe nokku makko on hanki mun, …ìe wa…óti wiide: \"Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O …ìi…ótinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wanaa Alla mo∆¥∆¥inoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  28,83,"∆äen galle laakara, Men wa…óanii …óe …ìen …ìe yi…óaa townitaare ka leydi, wanaa kadi bonnugol. Battane mo∆¥∆¥e …óen, ko fii gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  28,84,"Kala ardu…óo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, hino woodani mo ko …ìuri nde mo∆¥∆¥ude; kala kadi ardu…óo e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwu…ìe bon…ói …óin yo…ìetaake, si wanaa ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon"
